”和“NIJISANJI EN (New)”相关的图像。</em></p></blockquote><h2 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading" id="outline__1"> 210万人</h2><h3 id="outline__1_1" class="wp-block-heading" id="outline__1_1">菲莲</h3><figure class="wp-block-image"><img data-attachment-id="96320" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/filian-becomes-the-3rd-active-english-speaking-vtuber-in-history-to-reach-2-million-youtube-subscribers/filian_youtube_channel_14_july_2023/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/filian_youtube_channel_14_july_2023.jpg" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="filian_youtube_channel_14_july_2023" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/filian_youtube_channel_14_july_2023.jpg" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/filian_youtube_channel_14_july_2023.jpg" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/filian_youtube_channel_14_july_2023.jpg" alt="filian 频道订阅人数突破200万，成为活跃英语VTuber史上第三人" class="wp-image-96320"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> filian（截至2023年7月13日）<br> © 神话人才 2023</figcaption></figure><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td>人才名称</td><td>注册人数（较1个月前增减）</td></tr><tr><td>菲莲</td><td>210 万 (+110,000)</td></tr></tbody></table><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">截至2023年8月11日00:00</figcaption></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://youtube.com/channel/UCvjNdLLy5sinqD92Axk8w-g" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">filian</a> / <a href=